verses.text: \w For|strong="H3588"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* sons \w of|strong="H3068"\w* Core, \w a|strong="H3588"\w* psalm \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3588"\w* canticle. \w The|strong="H3588"\w* foundations thereof \w are|strong="H3068"\w* \w in|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* holy mountains:
\w The|strong="H3588"\w* Lord loveth \w the|strong="H3588"\w* gates \w of|strong="H0430"\w* Sion \w above|strong="H0413"\w* all \w the|strong="H3588"\w* tabernacles \w of|strong="H0430"\w* Jacob.
Glorious \w things|strong="H3605"\w* \w are|strong="H3117"\w* \w said|strong="H0413"\w* \w of|strong="H3117"\w* thee, \w O|strong="H0136"\w* city \w of|strong="H3117"\w* \w God|strong="H0136"\w*.

\w I|strong="H3588"\w* \w will|strong="H5650"\w* \w be|strong="H5315"\w* mindful \w of|strong="H5650"\w* Rahab \w and|strong="H5650"\w* \w of|strong="H5650"\w* Babylon knowing \w me|strong="H0413"\w*. Behold \w the|strong="H3588"\w* foreigners, \w and|strong="H5650"\w* Tyre, \w and|strong="H5650"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w people|strong="H5315"\w* \w of|strong="H5650"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* Ethiopians, these \w were|strong="H5650"\w* there.

Shall \w not|strong="H3588"\w* Sion say: \w This|strong="H3588"\w* \w man|strong="H3605"\w* \w and|strong="H7121"\w* \w that|strong="H3588"\w* \w man|strong="H3605"\w* \w is|strong="H3605"\w* born \w in|strong="H7121"\w* \w her|strong="H3605"\w*? \w and|strong="H7121"\w* \w the|strong="H3605"\w* Highest \w himself|strong="H7121"\w* hath founded \w her|strong="H3605"\w*.

\w The|strong="H3068"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w* \w shall|strong="H3068"\w* tell \w in|strong="H3068"\w* \w his|strong="H3068"\w* writings \w of|strong="H3068"\w* peoples \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w of|strong="H3068"\w* princes, \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w them|strong="H3068"\w* \w that|strong="H3068"\w* \w have|strong="H3068"\w* \w been|strong="H3068"\w* \w in|strong="H3068"\w* her.

\w The|strong="H3588"\w* dwelling \w in|strong="H3117"\w* thee \w is|strong="H3117"\w* \w as|strong="H3117"\w* \w it|strong="H7121"\w* \w were|strong="H3117"\w* \w of|strong="H3117"\w* \w all|strong="H3117"\w* rejoicing.
